/*
FURTHER READING

smoothing

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mollifier
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smoothstep
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flat_function
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bump_function
